title: American.Pie.5.The.Naked.Mile.Sountrack-DsG
description:
American Pie 5 The Naked Mile Soundtrack

There was never an official soundtrack released for this film. I managed to pick up a track list and got to work putting one together. Unfortunately, it uses a lot of smaller artists so tracks can be difficult to find. I managed to find 10 tracks out of the 34 listed. If anyone can find the missing tracks (at the reasonable quality and by the featured artist) that are not on this torrent then please let me know by leaving a comment and I will update the collection.

A track list can be found here: http://answers.yahoo.com/question/index?qid=20061231044443AAJwqIP

Please Seed, DsG!
